description:
It's RATS off in the DISTANCE! RAAAAATS. The Doom Company of Pater Badmūn have been run out of town by the doomed mob and find themselves climbing to a tower for the night... only to be met by the scurrying of starving, sick Rats. Tyler is back for more 1490 DOOM!
